WEBVTT

00:01.967 --> 00:04.500
Uh, Magnus...

00:04.500 --> 00:05.700
I think I'm going to throw up!

00:05.700 --> 00:06.967
This is ridiculous!

00:06.967 --> 00:08.867
Hold on, I've lost lateral control!

00:12.067 --> 00:14.467
Okay, this is really not going well!

00:14.467 --> 00:15.700
I know!

00:15.700 --> 00:16.801
No lift.

00:16.801 --> 00:17.801
I can't get any altitude!

00:17.801 --> 00:20.867
Bloody hell!

00:20.867 --> 00:22.300
Try hitting it with more sedation!

00:22.300 --> 00:24.001
Yeah, I'm already doing that!

00:24.001 --> 00:25.400
What the hell is wrong with...

00:27.967 --> 00:29.700
Magnus...

00:31.700 --> 00:33.534
Magnus, pull up.

00:33.534 --> 00:34.534
I can't!

00:34.534 --> 00:36.734
Pull up now!

00:36.734 --> 00:37.867
Dammit!

00:37.867 --> 00:39.867
Oh, this is going to be nasty.

00:43.333 --> 00:53.467
